msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Stop stalling and start explaining!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "P-Please, you got it all wrong!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Is this... a lover's quarrel?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "I know what you've been up to!\r\nI've seen how much money you spend!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Huh? That's, um..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "How often do you see her?\r\nDo you really love her!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "W-Well, talking to her\r\n<font_kind=yakuza_italic>does</font_kind> excite me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Huh? So you won't deny it?\r\nUgh, you're the lowest of the low!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Wait, I've never even met her, though!\r\nThat means I wasn't cheating!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "How can you say that!?\r\nNot like it matters. We're finished!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Ah! Wait, Yuka-chan!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Owww..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "Sorry, man!\r\nCrap, where's Yuka-chan?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "She's gone...\r\nDamn it all..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Hey, pull yourself together."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "But she's taking this all wrong.\r\nI just got a <font_kind=yakuza_italic>little</font_kind> hooked on live chat..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "Live... chat?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Yeah, you heard me.\r\nI've been spending all my time there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "Yuka-chan somehow thought\r\nI was cheating on her, though..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Uh-huh."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "But she's wrong, right!? Live chat isn't\r\ncheating, I just know it! Don't you agree?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Sorry, but I can't weigh in if I don't\r\nknow what you're talking about."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "Huh? You don't know live chat!?\r\nHow is that possible!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "It's exactly what it sounds like!\r\nYou know what a chat room is, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "Ch-Chat room..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Of course I know. That's a room\r\nfull of adorable kittens, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "No, that would be a <font_kind=yakuza_italic>cat</font_kind> room."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "A chat room, on the other hand, is\r\na handy way to talk to people online."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "A chat room, huh? It's where you go\r\nto have short conversations with people."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Sort of, but there's more to it than that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "A chat room refers specifically to\r\na handy way to talk to people online."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "A chat room... That's some kind of\r\nonline messaging group, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "Yes, you're totally right!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "As for live chat, it's a chat room made\r\nespecially for talking to cute girls."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "Hmm... So it's an online cabaret club?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "I guess you could say that...\r\nbut live chat is way better!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "After all, some things are off-limits at cabarets.\r\nY'know, the <font_kind=yakuza_italic>really good</font_kind> stuff."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "The... really good stuff?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "Have I piqued your interest?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah, maybe a little bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "Awesome! Man, just thinking about\r\nlive chat makes me wanna go again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "That's it! If you come with me to\r\nlive chat, I can teach you how to do it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Huh? Me...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Yup! My favorite net café's right over there,\r\nso just drop by when you're in the mood!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "I'll show you everything, and so will the girls!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "I'm no good with computers, though..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "Don't worry, I'll help you through it!\r\nOnward to the <font_kind=yakuza_italic>really good</font_kind> stuff!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Hm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Well, I'll be waiting for you!\r\nSee you over there!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah, I'll stop by at some point."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "Live chat, huh? I guess I <font_kind=yakuza_italic>am</font_kind> interested.\r\nI should poke my head into that net café..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "Welcome."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "We are a members only internet café."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "For only 5,000 yen a month, you'll get full access\r\nto our services. Would you like to join?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "Yeah, sign me up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "Thank you.\r\nUse this as your membership card."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "Please enjoy your stay."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "I'll come back another time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "I understand.\r\nWe look forward to your return."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Oh, there you are!\r\nI'm all ready, so let's go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Okay.\r\nI don't know what to do, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "Don't worry, I'll be by your side the whole time!\r\nCome on, let's get chatting!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "I recommend DMM if you want to live chat. \r\nDouble-click this icon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "When it comes to live chat, this is the site.\r\nStart by double-clicking on that icon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Icon? Um...\r\nSo... Like this...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "Perfect! You're connected to the site now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "Just click a girl's photo to start chatting.\r\nEasy, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "Oh, and you can send messages by\r\njust typing them out and pressing enter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "Typing's not really my strong suit..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "Ah! That one looks pretty cute, doesn't she?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "Agreed. Let's go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "All right, you're in!\r\nLive chat starts now. Simple, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "Hm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "Hello there!\r\nIs this your first time?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "H-Hey, why's she talking to me!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "Don't worry, this is how it works.\r\nJust type your response out to her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "R-Right. But... how am I\r\nsupposed to respond to that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "How about a compliment or a greeting?\r\n\"You're cute,\" or maybe \"Sup?\"!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "H-Here I go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "You... are... very... cute..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "W-Well?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "You think I'm cute?\r\nI'm so glad!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "Look, she's blushing!\r\nYou're doing it, you're doing it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "Huh.\r\nSo this is live chat..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "Yup! Now get those keys clacking!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "Uh, what?\r\nIs that <font_kind=yakuza_italic>really</font_kind> what I should put?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "\"S\"... \"U\"... \"P\"... \"?\"...\r\nThere."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "I think I messed up..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "Hey there!\r\n'Sup to you, too!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "Whoa, she liked that!\r\nYou're doing it, you're doing it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "Huh.\r\nSo this is how live chat goes..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "Yup yup! Now get those keys clacking!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "This... is... so... much... fun..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "It's fun for me, too! <symbol=heart_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "Dude, you're like some kinda chat wizard!\r\nShe's totally loving it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "I wasn't sure how this would turn out,\r\nbut it's actually kinda fun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "Ain't it?\r\nBut the <font_kind=yakuza_italic>real</font_kind> best of live chat is yet to come!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "Huh? There's more?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "You bet there is.\r\nAh, here it comes!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "You've been so sweet to me today...\r\nWhy don't I make up for it? <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "Sh-She's stripping!\r\nHey, what do I do now!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "You're getting a private show!\r\nThis is the true live chat now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "Wh-Whoa...!\r\nLive chat is... amazing..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "Damn right it is!\r\nNow let's get the show started!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "O-Okay."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "So curvy!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "Whoa..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "Tell her to show us more!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "Show... me... some... more... please..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "Wonderful..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "She really is..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "That was great."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "So what did you think?\r\nPretty damn fun, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "Yeah, how do I put this...\r\nIt was refreshing, to say the least."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "I can understand how you got\r\nwrapped up in all this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "Right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "But no matter how fun it is,\r\nyou shouldn't ignore your girlfriend."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||||4"
msgid "I've actually been considering that...\r\nand I've reached a turning point."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||||4"
msgid "Yup! I've decided I don't need\r\na girlfriend anymore!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "Live chat's way more enticing than a girlfriend\r\ncould ever be! Don't you think?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "Real-life women can be moody,\r\nbut chat ladies are always energetic and cute!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "Besides, having a girlfriend would\r\njust cut into my chat time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "So I'm better off not having one at all!\r\nThat way, I can chat forever without regret!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "131||||4"
msgid "Well, I guess that's one angle..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "A new me is born today!\r\nI'm gonna devote my life to live chat!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "Speaking of, I should log back in there.\r\nWe should talk some more later!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "Maybe next time we see each\r\nother will be in a chat room!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "Bye now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "Uh... Yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "Live chat...\r\nWhat a rush..."
msgstr ""

